description:
Yesterday I tried not to be influenced by other people's projects, so I made my project before looking at others. Today I tried the opposite approach: I started with a tour of other people's gardens, I picked my favorite flowers, put them in my backpack and planted them in my project. I see it as a way to celebrate diversity and getting inspired by others.

Thanks to: 
@mizzpeters @karenb @ClarendonRoadCC @carlapoppi @chrise07
@clarimer @edmondmm @PinkGoldPeachyKeen @mres @colemantigers and all the unstuck friends for their beautiful flowers and inspiration!
